            <title>[CASSANDRA-16484] Audit consumption/removal of ApplicationState padding</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-16484</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It looks like some padding states, which should never be removed or changed, has occurred in ApplicationState.  This ticket will serve to correct that.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
